Damn.

394
00:47:09,651 --> 00:47:12,184
Is the trap ready?

395
00:47:13,484 --> 00:47:15,217
Let's see it.

396
00:47:25,384 --> 00:47:27,050
(Edee grunts)

397
00:47:30,150 --> 00:47:31,217
Better?

398
00:47:31,250 --> 00:47:33,617
