And then pull it.

430
00:49:53,684 --> 00:49:56,250
(sighs) Okay.

431
00:49:57,484 --> 00:50:00,417
That's it. (exhales, sniffs)

432
00:50:01,651 --> 00:50:04,050
♪ ♪

433
00:50:26,617 --> 00:50:29,017
