461
00:53:42,217 --> 00:53:44,050
And it was painful,
I have to say.

462
00:53:44,084 --> 00:53:46,517
Mm, there's a lot more
where that came from.

463
00:53:46,551 --> 00:53:49,017
- (chuckles): Oh, no.
- Oh, yeah.

