500
00:56:02,484 --> 00:56:05,883
I have nieces.

501
00:56:05,917 --> 00:56:08,017
They're my family now.

502
00:56:08,651 --> 00:56:10,917
My wife's sister's kids.

503
00:56:14,250 --> 00:56:16,983
My wife and my daughter
were killed

504
00:56:17,017 --> 00:56:18,983
