there than here.

519
00:57:44,484 --> 00:57:45,950
That may sound...

520
00:57:45,983 --> 00:57:47,351
It doesn't make
any sense, but...

521
00:57:47,384 --> 00:57:50,250
No, it does.

522
00:57:50,284 --> 00:57:52,451
It does to me.

523
00:57:58,117 --> 00:58:02,983
If you don't want
to talk about the past,

524
00:58:03,017 --> 00:58:08,351
